_sText: Wow.. ages since i made a map.. anyway.. kz_ map for cs source. It's not very big but it's still challenging in some areas. Still in beta release. Have fun. All textures are within the bsp, so no crappy downloading textures or disconnect errors :-) Give it a run before you base it on my poor screenshots ;) There's a nice surprise for the first to finish just before they do :-)
